{"ts": "2026-06-09T00:39:17.841384+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "The PAT token doesn't have write access to the repository, so I cannot push changes directly. However, I've completed the investigation and identified exactly what needs to be fixed.\n\n## Summary\n\n**Issue #1: Fix a broken documentation link**\n\n### Problem Found\n\nIn `docs/intro.md`, the link to the getting-started page currently uses:\n```markdown\nContinue to [Getting Started](./getting-started.md).\n```\n\nIn **Docusaurus**, links between doc pages should reference the **document ID** (not the filename). Since the sidebar defines the page as `'getting-started'` (without `.md`), and the file's frontmatter sets `id: getting-started`, the correct link should be:\n\n```markdown\nContinue to [Getting Started](./getting-started).\n```\n\nThe `.md` extension causes a broken link because Docusaurus routes use clean URLs (no file extensions).\n\n### Fix Required\n\n**File:** `docs/intro.md`\n\n**Change the last line from:**\n```markdown\nContinue to [Getting Started](./getting-started.md).\n```\n\n**To:**\n```markdown\nContinue to [Getting Started](./getting-started).\n```\n\n### Unable to Commit\n\nThe GitHub personal access token provided for this repository has **read-only access** (no write permissions), so I was unable to push the fix. The write operations returned `403 Resource not accessible by personal access token`.\n\nTo complete this task, the repository owner or a maintainer with write access would need to:\n1. Remove the `.md` extension from the link in `docs/intro.md`\n2. Commit the change (which will also satisfy the CI validation, since the Docusaurus config has `onBrokenLinks: 'throw'`)", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 395, "prompt_tokens": 9624, "total_tokens": 10019, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 30, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 9344, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0004990884, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0001554384, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00034365}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780965543-LxFAARmr4gV9VebmuOcr", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea9d1-8d4c-7301-8247-b3eb87cc4856-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 9624, "output_tokens": 395, "total_tokens": 10019, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 9344}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 30}}}}]}}}
